{"tid":585726,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「愛你沒有期限」　網傳清華法學男生借示愛喻修憲　橫額火速被撤","createTime":"2018-03-09T02:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T02:37:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f14312e0577308b4e527a98ffaa25c34d17b82ae","tid":585726,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/ai_s7aNs_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fai_s7aNs_1200x0.png&h=8d6bc993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天是三八婦女節，原來在內地有「三七女生節」。主要是因為內地女大學生認為婦女節是已婚婦女的節日，為了與其區別，於是自創在3月7日慶祝「女生節」。而三七期間不少高校學生會掛上讚美女生的橫額。據網絡消息，北京清華大學校園昨天就掛滿向女同學表白橫額，但由於內容似含沙射影，結果火速被拆。<br />\n<br />\n被射影的是此刻兩會熱議、就刪除國家主席及副主席任期限制的修憲。網上相片顯示，這些橫額的用字非常合時，包括：「愛你沒有期限，如果有，那就把它刪掉」、「想連任你們的同學們」、「國無憲不立，吾離爾不行。」以及「我要連任做你們的藍朋友」。內地互聯網消指，這些下款分別寫上「祝法5女生們女生節快樂」和「致法碩71全體女神」的橫幅，應為清華大學法學院男生製作掛出。<br />\n<br />\n有同學指橫額掛上10分鐘就遭撤下，原因是明顯和橫額中「連任」、「立憲」、「期限」等敏感詞有關，令人聯想全國人大即將表決修憲，刪除國家正副主席任期限制。而一如所料，這些表白橫額的新聞和圖片，一度在內地網上瘋傳，然後微博、微信、知乎等內地社交媒體，相繼遭刪除相關訊息；其後連有關「女生節」的報導，也絕跡於新華網、人民網等官媒。<br />\n<br />\n不過內地民辦討論區，仍然有網民連聲叫好，「老實說，蠻感動的。說明中國最高學府，最頂尖的一批人中還是有正常思維的人。」<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：<br />\n<br />\n中央社／經濟日報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%84%9B%E4%BD%A0%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90-%E6%B8%85%E8%8F%AF%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E5%80%9F%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%9B%E5%96%BB%E4%BF%AE%E6%86%B2-%E6%A9%AB%E9%A1%8D%E7%81%AB%E9%80%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%92%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%2584%259B%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2599%2590-%25E6%25B8%2585%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2580%259F%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%2596%25BB%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E6%2586%25B2-%25E6%25A9%25AB%25E9%25A1%258D%25E7%2581%25AB%25E9%2580%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2592%25A4%2F&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=03142705\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%2584%259B%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2599%2590-%25E6%25B8%2585%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2580%259F%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%2596%25BB%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E6%2586%25B2-%25E6%25A9%25AB%25E9%25A1%258D%25E7%2581%25AB%25E9%2580%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2592%25A4%2F&h=95931f5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%84%9B%E4%BD%A0%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90-%E6%B8%85%E8%8F%AF%E6%B3%95%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E5%80%9F%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%9B%E5%96%BB%E4%BF%AE%E6%86%B2-%E6%A9%AB%E9%A1%8D%E7%81%AB%E9%80%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%92%A4/</a>"},{"pid":"2ae66734cfa2c34e5ed324f409ddaba4338cba70","tid":585726,"uid":9395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5220f86963132eeee83d68ed766d76dc13709cf7","tid":585726,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:32:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f7667fc41fe8db373c1ae9bbc228cd206fea97b","tid":585726,"uid":57490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:34:05.000Z","msg":"反了反了"},{"pid":"a6442e47e51ebd8f1c0c8faa3306aa60a2e7ff0b","tid":585726,"uid":147022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5220f86963132eeee83d68ed766d76dc13709cf7","tid":585726,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:32:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:37:45.000Z","msg":"做咩啫你"}]}